Date: Sun, 17 May 2026 18:02:14 +0600
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add Kimi Code CLI support

Add Kimi Code CLI as a new backend executor using ACP protocol.
Supports model override, yolo auto-approve, and session resumption.
Includes frontend icons and JSON schema generation.
